{"tid":1790311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布RubberBand係香港第一樂隊","createTime":"2019-12-20T01:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T11:17:02.000Z","uid":271367,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"db0115f01d34810bf7b76e127fcee84fd000f786","tid":1790311,"uid":271367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:51:23.000Z","msg":"出左首歌～漫長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MR9DVMu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMR9DVMu.png&h=27c05205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代流轉這刻在這地 是否選中我 <br />\n如何殘缺結果尚未到期 那甘心放棄</span></span><br />\n  <br />\n又一天 惺忪雙眼漸開 仍舊離家很遠 <br />\n又開始 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">博弈在人海 被硝煙將腳步掩蓋</span></span>  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">教我要怎麼方不害怕 理據堂皇地作假 <br />\n如果 明晨 是更黑一晚 應該怎麼進化  </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時代流轉這刻在這地 是否選中我 <br />\n如何殘缺結果尚未到期 那甘心放棄  <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又一晚 不懂得去 進睡 還是忙於心碎 <br />\n又開始 浸沒在淚水 乍醒始終惡夢裡  </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n信仰強拆中消磨 遍野仍無盡星火 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可如初 可做我</span></span> 誰能被隔阻<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n時代流轉這刻在這地 是否選中我 <br />\n始終一天結果尚未到期 那甘心放棄  <br />\n<br />\n時代流轉這刻在這地 若果選中我 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如何殘缺結果尚未到期 說不出放棄</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kM_DLxId8ok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkM_DLxId8ok&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5T2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5c7768f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kM_DLxId8ok</a><br />\n<br />\n寫得咁好，得個幾千view。快去睇啦！"},{"pid":"130f7cb2a2fa23eed8450d9b1b2198a91866dafe","tid":1790311,"uid":10352